<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>879</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>gāng qiáng qǐ lái 迦南879</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 gāng qiáng qǐ lái, gāng qiáng qǐ lái, gāng qiáng qǐ lái.
 shén de ér nǚ ya, gāng qiáng qǐ lái, jiǎo bù cháo qián jìn.
 bù wàng jì zhǔ yé sū de fēn fù, chuán fú yīn gěi wàn mín tīng.
 yé sū jī dū de jiào huì, bì néng wán chéng dà shǐ mìng.
 zhēn jīn bù pà huǒ lái liàn, gè gè dōu zuò zhǔ de jīng bīng.
 zhè shì yī gè dà shí dài, yé sū yǐ dé shèng. a
 wǒ men yào fèn yǒng.</lyrics>
</song>